=====================================================================
See Npcs/Valerius Sec. III for the full, current leverage web (Elisif, Orion, the Crown
clock, the Davinia/Ismara audience). This section covers faction-level assets only.

1. THE DOUBLE AGENT (Orion) — STATUS CHANGED. Orion wore the Ring of the Pale Regent and
