3. THE DOSSIER (Tax Collectors) — a sealed dossier tying the party to the murder of
   Imperial tax collectors and their recovered badges, from earlier in the campaign.
   STATUS: dormant/likely stale — no recent scene has referenced it. Keep it in reserve
   as a blackmail lever if a use for it resurfaces; do not assume it is still his primary
   hook (that role now belongs to the Orion leash and the Elisif courtship).

